Under LiteSpeed with OPcache, this PHP endpoint held ~24,000 req/s with a p99 around 6 ms — slower than both JS runtimes per-core, but it is already behind a mature SAPI that handles connection pooling, process management, and is sitting under the same Cloudflare cache.
